long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Socely is a LinkedIn Automation Software that helps to automate the process of LinkedIn outreach by doing routine tasks such as sending invites and messages. Socely has its own CRM inside to work with sales leads and communicate with them.
The extension allows authorise in Socely and get access to LinkedIn information.
